Module 2 6. WACP to find the sum of natural numbers from 1 to N using while loop. #include<stdio.h> void main() { int n, i=1, sum=0; printf(“Enter the value of n”
); scanf(“%d”, &n); while (i<=n) { sum=sum+i; i=i++; } printf(“%d”, sum); } 7. WAP to find sum of odd numbers from 1 to N using do-while loop. include<stdio.h> void main() { int n, i=1, sum=0; printf(“Enter the value of n”
); scanf(“%d”, &n); do { sum=sum+i; i = i + 2; } while (i<=n); printf(“Sum of odd numbers is %d”, sum); } 8. WACP to check whether a given number is even or odd using if-else statement. include<stdio.h> void main() { int n; printf(“Enter a number”
); scanf(“%d”, &n); if(n%2==0) printf(“The given number is Even
”); else printf(“The given number is Odd
”); } 29 2020-21
